law.catch_line: Use of administrative savings from 1996 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 1.
law.text: Subsequent administrative savings as a result of the implementation of 1996 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 1 shall be used to defray the special fund assessment on all employers in the Commonwealth.
law.history: Created 1996 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 1, sec. 85, effective December 12, 1996.
